6.20	The_Easter_Parade	The Easter Parade	The Easter Parade is a novel by American writer Richard Yates. First published in 1976, Yates' fifth book concerns the tragic lives of two sisters. Some consider the book, along with Revolutionary Road, to be Yates' finest work.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/1/19/Easter_parade_yates.jpg/200px-Easter_parade_yates.jpg
